data.description: Welcome home to your country paradise.   The first thing you see when you drive into this gorgeous 10.98 acre property is your 2 acre pond full of wildlife. The rest of this expansive property is a nice mix of woods with walking trails/pasture/mowed lawn area. When you walk into this wonderful country home you'll be greeted by a newly remodeled kitchen complete with quartz countertops, new appliances and knotty alder cabinets. The great room boasts dramatic vaulted ceilings with a floor to ceiling fireplace. Once you're able to make it through your beautiful kitchen/great room head outside to the huge deck overlooking your park-like yard. Furnace and A/C are approx 5 yrs old / Generac generator installed / huge unfinished lower level ready for expansion.
